      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape it still smells brand new! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent anywhere. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
