    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is flawless; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, with no signs of wear on the bolsters, and the interior still retains that unmistakable 'new car' scent. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 47250.0,
